transcription: Dung beetle, dung beetle, smelly old dung beetle. Dung beetle sleeping in the dung. Ow, ow, ow! Idiot, clodful, brainless brat! My name is Alice, not brat or dung beetle or beetle. Alice.  Go up that road to the manor. They are hiring boys to help with the threshing. Alice! We was wondering where you had got to! I am the ingirl. And a prettier ingirl the world has ever saw.  She ran away. You seen her? She was not as stupid as some I had had. And better company. But perhaps her going was for the best. She was not what I needed. Because it failed. Because she gave up. I think you're about to have a child. I can do no more. This baby will not come out. Let me try.  ah
